CONDITIONAL STATEMENTS
IF, ELIF, ELSE

LOOPS
FOR, WHILE

FUNCTION
PRINT()

HANDS-ON SAMPLES
IF STATEMENTS
/*
a = 7
b = 8

if a < b:
    print(a, "is smaller than", b)
*/
ELSE STATEMENTS
/*
a = 8
b = 8

if a < b:
    print(a, "is smaller than", b)

elif a > b:
    print(a, "is bigger than", b)

else:
    print(a, "is equal to", b)
*/

ELIF STATEMENTS (YOU CAN ADD AS MANY ELIF STATEMENTS AS YOU WANT)
/*
a = 7
b = 8

if a < b:
    print(a, "is smaller than", b)

elif a > b:
    print(a, "is bigger than", b)
*/
